Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.64,0:00:05.15,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}From a different point of view, even an imposing\N wall blocking your path is just a large door.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.15,0:00:08.02,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A baseball came flying in, and a house\Nbecomes a case flipped on its head!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.02,0:00:09.73,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Something’s not right about this room!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.73,0:00:11.19,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.19,0:00:12.82,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}{\c&HFFAAAA}and looks like a kid but\N has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.82,0:00:14.70,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}{\c&HFFAAAA}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.81,0:02:12.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\i1}Sensei{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.28,0:02:16.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Well, if it isn’t the editor, Shimaki-kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.74,0:02:20.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Geez, don’t “Well, if it isn’t Shimaki-kun{\i0}” me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.16,0:02:22.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}So, what are you here about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.28,0:02:25.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}W-What are you saying, {\i1}Sensei{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 1,0:02:25.54,0:02:31.42,Signs,,0,0,0,,Toshihisa Manda (53)\NNovelist
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.54,0:02:31.42,Signs,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.54,0:02:27.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I’m just joking, don’t worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.87,0:02:29.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Don’t scare me like that…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.62,0:02:31.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}It’s about the manuscript, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.00,0:02:34.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Yes, that’s right, Manda-sensei{\i0}…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.04,0:02:37.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I’m begging you, don’t play jokes on me…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.67,0:02:39.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}This is a real problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.72,0:02:45.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}The printers can only wait two more hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.97,0:02:49.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Two hours will be more than enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.98,0:02:51.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Two hours?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.69,0:02:53.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{I’ve already finished the climax…}I just have one hurdle left to jump,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.48,0:02:56.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}and after that, it just leaves the epilogue.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.90,0:02:58.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.40,0:02:59.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.86,0:03:03.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Please trust me. We’ve known each other so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.04,0:03:09.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Hey, Novel-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.54,0:03:13.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I’m counting on you to keep an eye on {\i1}Sensei{\i0}!{extended?}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.92,0:03:16.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Don’t let him make a run for it! \NIf he tries to get away, bite him!{possibly, “bite him if he tries to get away”?}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.26,0:03:23.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I’ll be waiting in the lobby by the lifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.55,0:03:26.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Please call me when you’re done!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.18,0:03:28.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Sure, will do.
