Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.09,0:04:48.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Yes… Two more hours…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.89,0:04:49.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.72,0:04:51.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Seems like he can pull it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.93,0:04:57.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Yeah, that’s what he said.\N It’ll probably be all right…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.35,0:04:59.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Yeah, don’t worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.27,0:05:00.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Here’s what he wrote…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.50,0:05:19.00,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The Ace of Teitan Primary School’s Class 1-B,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.00,0:05:21.05,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}the prince of pitchers{not sure about this word}, Genta Kojima,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.05,0:05:23.63,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}aims to remain undefeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.13,0:05:27.68,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Two outs, bases loaded.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.68,0:05:30.47,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Mitsuhiko Tsubaraya’s in full form!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.89,0:05:32.51,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And here’s the first pitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.98,0:05:35.84,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.27,0:05:42.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.03,0:05:45.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I’m counting on you, Edogawa-kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.61,0:05:47.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Counting… for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.82,0:05:49.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}The ball, the ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.90,0:05:53.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}A-All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.16,0:05:54.54,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.34,0:06:06.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.64,0:06:12.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}That was awesome, Conan-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.26,0:06:14.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Yes… {\i1}if{\i0} we were playing football.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.10,0:06:16.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}You have to catch the ball in your glove!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.89,0:06:18.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}This isn’t football!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.38,0:06:21.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}You got something against baseball, Conan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.98,0:06:26.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}That’s right, Conan-kun{\i0}!\N Take this seriously, geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.99,0:06:29.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}My bad, my bad…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.91,0:06:31.03,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What am I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.03,0:06:35.66,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}After years of playing football, I’m used to doing everything with my legs…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.51,0:06:53.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be10}{\i1}Sensei{\i0}…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.93,0:06:54.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I’ve been waiting for you…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.35,0:06:57.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}They got my neck on the line now…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.89,0:07:00.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Manda-sensei{\i0}…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.14,0:07:02.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Those clothes…
Dialogue: 1,0:07:02.23,0:07:06.14,Signs,,0,0,0,,Kohei Haramoto (28)\NManda’s protegé
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.23,0:07:06.14,Signs,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.23,0:07:05.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Did you sneak out of a hotel again…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.40,0:07:07.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}…disguised as a valet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.73,0:07:08.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}You really like doing that, don’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.99,0:07:12.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Yeah, they tried to lock me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.87,0:07:14.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}This was the quickest way to get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.12,0:07:22.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}This way, nobody noticed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.79,0:07:25.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Hey, you brought Novel-kun with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.75,0:07:27.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Novel, Novel!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.59,0:07:31.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}That’s a kitty… It’s me…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.80,0:07:37.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I couldn’t leave him. Novel\N panics if one of us isn’t around.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.02,0:07:42.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}More importantly…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.60,0:07:44.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}…have you finished the manuscript?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.40,0:07:47.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Yeah, I polished it off…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.73,0:07:48.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}…six hours ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.15,0:07:51.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Six hours ago?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.90,0:07:57.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}But when I called you from the hotel, you said you “just needed a bit more time”!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.99,0:08:04.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I was just messing with you. {You wouldn’t stop riding me…}Your voice sounds hilarious when you’re desperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.42,0:08:06.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Come on, Haramoto-kun{\i0}…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.46,0:08:08.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Can’t I at least have a little fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.84,0:08:12.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Being your ghostwriter can get stressful, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.05,0:08:17.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}But as long as you pay me the big bucks…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.10,0:08:19.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I’ve got no complaints!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.48,0:08:26.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.31,0:08:29.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Your latest novel!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.32,0:08:33.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}With a happy ending, just as you requested!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.61,0:08:35.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Ah, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.16,0:08:40.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}So, er… Did you talk to your editor about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.16,0:08:47.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Once I hand this off to him, we’re going to have a meeting at my place to discuss the next piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.63,0:08:51.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I’ll bring him across the street to meet you after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.59,0:08:56.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Really? Thank you so much! I’m so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.93,0:09:01.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{But if you get published under your own name, you’ll want to quit this gig…}But once you’ve had your début,\N I’ll probably have to retire.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.22,0:09:05.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Don’t worry, I can keep ghosting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.85,0:09:09.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I’ll be writing detective novels, which is nothing like what you write!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.44,0:09:11.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I’ll even use a different writing style.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.73,0:09:14.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}A different…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.36,0:09:17.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}To be honest, I’m almost done…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.99,0:09:21.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}with my début novel!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.12,0:09:27.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Want to give it a lookover? You’ll see, it really feels like it was written by somebody else.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.04,0:09:30.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Soon I’ll be a real novelist!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.54,0:09:34.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}And if my work sells, I’ll have more\N money for my collections…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.84,0:09:39.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Oh, yeah. You {\i1}are{\i0} quite the collector, aren’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.09,0:09:39.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.01,0:09:44.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I’ve loved collecting stuff since I was a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.14,0:09:46.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}But the item I want now…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.27,0:09:49.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}…is the Akutayama Award for New Writers!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.90,0:09:54.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}You’re one of the judges, so I’m a shoo-in, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.07,0:09:59.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}If I win that one, collecting other\N awards will be a piece of cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.41,0:10:05.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Speaking of collections, I finally got something else I’ve been missing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.25,0:10:06.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.47,0:10:22.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}It feels so good…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.89,0:10:24.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}…to complete the set!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.47,0:10:27.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}That’s nice to hear…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:48.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\a6}“Working — Do Not Enter!”
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.12,0:10:51.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Come on, Novel! Time to head back to the hotel…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.42,0:10:52.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Novel?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.96,0:10:55.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Novel? Novel?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.26,0:11:02.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Where are you, Novel?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.76,0:11:03.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.26,0:11:06.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Novel? Novel!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.14,0:11:08.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Novel? Novel?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.52,0:11:10.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Novel! Novel!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.23,0:11:14.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Where are you, Novel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.19,0:11:17.23,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.74,0:11:21.57,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I’ve got to hurry… To hurry back to the hotel…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.07,0:11:24.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be10}{\i1}Sensei{\i0}? Manda-sensei{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.28,0:11:26.37,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If I don’t get back to the hotel,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.37,0:11:28.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be10}{\i1}Sensei{\i0}! {\i1}Sensei{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.83,0:11:30.83,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}my alibi…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.83,0:11:33.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be10}{\i1}Sensei{\i0}! Manda-sensei{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.25,0:11:35.46,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.46,0:11:38.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be10}{\i1}Sensei{\i0}! It’s been two hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.96,0:11:41.68,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What do I do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.68,0:11:45.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be10}{\i1}Sensei{\i0}! Manda-sensei{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.98,0:11:57.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\i1}Sensei{\i0}! Manda-sensei{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.61,0:12:05.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\i1}Sensei{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.32,0:12:08.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Geez, what a nuisance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.37,0:12:11.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I was just going over my last revision!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.29,0:12:14.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Oh… I see! Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.54,0:12:18.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Frankly, I’ve impressed even myself this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.55,0:12:19.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.80,0:12:21.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.51,0:12:24.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}And thanks for the hard work!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.55,0:12:27.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Say, is Novel-kun{\i0} okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.26,0:12:30.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}He always comes out to greet me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.68,0:12:32.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}He’s awfully quiet…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.73,0:12:34.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Oh…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.85,0:12:38.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}He’s sleeping in his carrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.65,0:12:40.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}In his carrier…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.32,0:12:43.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Seems that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.20,0:12:46.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Well, I’d better get back to the office to look this over!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.87,0:12:53.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Why don’t you read it in my room and e-mail it to the printer from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.71,0:12:55.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}That’ll save you some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.04,0:13:03.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Afterwards, we can go to my place\N and talk about my next novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.26,0:13:07.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I didn’t think you had anything planned after this…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.64,0:13:11.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I’m sure you’ll enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.01,0:13:15.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}It’s an entirely new genre for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.44,0:13:19.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}A mystery?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.98,0:13:22.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}But you specialise in period fiction!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.86,0:13:24.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}You’re not pulling my leg, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.95,0:13:26.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.15,0:13:30.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}But I’ve always wanted to challenge\N myself with a mystery novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.33,0:13:33.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}You have?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.58,0:13:38.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I’m looking forward to it. \NI can’t wait to read it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.38,0:13:40.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Right, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.25,0:13:45.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\i1}Sensei{\i0}, please, tell me more about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.42,0:13:49.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I’ve already thought up a detective character.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.89,0:13:52.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I’ll tell you all about it at the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.93,0:13:57.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Oh, no, tell me! Don’t leave me hanging.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.39,0:13:59.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Well… well…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.56,0:14:02.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Novel-kun{\i0} is awfully quiet today…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.82,0:14:04.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.07,0:14:07.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}U-Uh, well…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.57,0:14:09.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}He was running around all day…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.57,0:14:11.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}…so he must be tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.58,0:14:13.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}No need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.70,0:14:15.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}You’re right…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.59,0:14:29.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Okay, hold on a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.51,0:14:32.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I need to tidy up a bit…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.80,0:14:35.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Oh, sure. I’ll wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.15,0:14:41.40,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Novel!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.40,0:14:44.36,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Novel! Novel!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.20,0:14:50.11,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Novel!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.41,0:15:00.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ah, Novel, you’re back! Good boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.75,0:15:05.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Now it’s all in place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.30,0:15:10.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I’ve completed the perfect crime…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.09,0:15:14.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Right, Novel?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.35,0:15:18.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.94,0:15:26.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}W-What was that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.69,0:15:32.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I think a window broke in the house across the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.66,0:15:36.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Looks like some kids were playing baseball and hit a ball into a window.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.87,0:15:38.87,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.58,0:15:42.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Geez…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.54,0:15:44.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}You swing too hard, Genta-kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.83,0:15:48.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I didn’t do it on purpose! It bounced away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.67,0:15:51.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}You can’t tell the ball where it can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.55,0:15:54.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Nobody’s answering the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.18,0:15:56.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}But it looks like somebody’s at home…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.35,0:16:00.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Maybe the ball hit the person inside the house and knocked them out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.73,0:16:07.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}There’s no way to know without going inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.69,0:16:08.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.61,0:16:13.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}“Huh”? Err…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.45,0:16:14.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Haibara-san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.99,0:16:17.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I had a feeling it was unlocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.58,0:16:21.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Excuse us…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.58,0:16:23.87,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Well, it’s a good excuse to go in, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.46,0:16:28.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The room the ball entered must be…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.55,0:16:30.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}H-Hey, Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.84,0:16:32.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Should we go in?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.80,0:16:36.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Conan-kun{\i0}, this is a home invasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.01,0:16:37.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Conan-kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.93,0:16:39.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Haibara-san{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.81,0:16:42.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Looks like we’ve got no other choice, don’t you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.69,0:16:46.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Excuse us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.90,0:16:49.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Excuse me…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.82,0:16:52.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Is anyone home?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.15,0:16:54.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.11,0:16:56.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}We’re not suspicious people…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.95,0:16:59.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Huh? Something’s weird about this room…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.95,0:17:04.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Yes, but I can’t put my finger on it…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.75,0:17:07.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Isn’t it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.13,0:17:07.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.92,0:17:12.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}The toy cars on the shelves…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.01,0:17:12.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}The figures…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.71,0:17:14.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}…and the books…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.51,0:17:16.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}…are almost all upside-down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.38,0:17:18.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.30,0:17:23.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Did my ball do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.39,0:17:31.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Maybe your ball warped the space inside the house, causing a supernatural phenomenon…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.73,0:17:37.32,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}{Of course not!}Mitsuhiko, something {\i1}is{\i0} off,\N but don’t get too carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.32,0:17:38.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The ball Genta hit…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.20,0:17:41.41,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I won’t lose this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.41,0:17:45.37,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Here it comes, Genta-kun{\i0}! Hit it if you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.37,0:17:48.12,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I can hit anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.84,0:17:51.75,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Edogawa-kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.75,0:17:52.21,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Conan-kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.59,0:17:56.59,FlashThoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh, crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.59,0:17:57.93,FlashThoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}That was a pretty strong one!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.93,0:18:01.47,FlashThoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Oh, geez, Genta hit it {\i1}really{\i0} hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.86,0:18:19.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Genta’s ball just happened to\N go in through an open window.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.16,0:18:22.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}But we heard something smash!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.83,0:18:26.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}The ball must’ve hit a vase or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.62,0:18:29.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}A-Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.58,0:18:33.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}What if it’s really expensive?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.00,0:18:37.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}And I’ve already blown my allowance this week…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.13,0:18:39.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}To know how much whatever we broke costs,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.88,0:18:42.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}we’ll have to ask whoever lives here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.72,0:18:48.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}The ball should be in this room…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.31,0:18:53.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Of course…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.44,0:18:56.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}That’s just if the guy who lives here…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.20,0:19:05.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}…can still talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.88,0:19:20.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.22,0:19:23.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}It’s no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.22,0:19:27.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{And it’s only been an hour or two since he died.}Given the rigor mortis{that’s rigor mortis, isn’t it? -uso.}, he’s probably been dead for an hour or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.64,0:19:32.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I see fragments from a vase\N scattered around the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.94,0:19:36.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I bet he was hit on the back of the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.19,0:19:40.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}You don’t mean…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.78,0:19:44.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}The ball I hit bumped into the vase…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.20,0:19:50.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}…and knocked it onto the guy’s head?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.50,0:19:53.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}G-Genta-kun{\i0}…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.00,0:19:54.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I’m doomed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.75,0:19:56.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}What do I do? What do I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.67,0:19:59.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}What now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.92,0:20:01.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Don’t be an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.13,0:20:04.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}You hit that ball just a few minutes ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.55,0:20:06.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Not an {\i1}hour{\i0} ago, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.55,0:20:09.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}What now? What… now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.85,0:20:14.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Looks like your ball hit that vase over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.94,0:20:17.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}That’s good, right, Genta?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.44,0:20:19.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}What a relief…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.98,0:20:24.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Then this means someone struck him from behind…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.32,0:20:27.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Yeah. He was hit with this vase\N
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.66,0:20:30.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}while he was looking through this drawer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.66,0:20:35.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}How do you know that he\N was looking through that drawer?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.17,0:20:40.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Look at the edge of the drawer. It’s dented!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.59,0:20:46.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}The body collapsed on it after he was hit from behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.05,0:20:53.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}He’d probably opened the drawer to either put something in or to take something out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.69,0:20:54.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.77,0:20:56.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}You’re so smart, Conan-kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.69,0:20:58.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}It’s the room next door that confuses me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.94,0:21:05.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Yeah. Most of the toys, models and books on the shelves are turned upside-down.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.11,0:21:10.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}If the killer did that, then what was it for?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.70,0:21:11.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.50,0:21:17.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}What are you kids doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.75,0:21:20.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}H-Haramoto-kun{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.50,0:21:23.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Is that Haramoto-kun{\i0} on the floor?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.59,0:21:26.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Hey, Haramoto-kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.30,0:21:27.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Haramoto-kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.59,0:21:28.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Haramoto-kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.14,0:21:31.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.26,0:21:33.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Call the police and an ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.27,0:21:35.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}S-Sure, right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.27,0:21:40.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}You kids need to clear out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.02,0:21:41.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Uh… Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.28,0:21:45.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Kitty!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.36,0:21:50.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}How’d you get in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.16,0:21:50.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Kitty…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.79,0:21:54.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Don’t touch my cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.38,0:22:04.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}C’mon, out! Out!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.01,0:22:07.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}You’ll have to give a report when the police arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.21,0:22:07.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\a6}What’s his problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.13,0:22:09.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\a6}He didn’t have to be that rude to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.22,0:22:10.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Tell me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.60,0:22:12.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.26,0:22:14.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Uh, yeah…
