Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.00,0:24:02.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Never mind that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.54,0:24:04.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Didn’t you notice yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.29,0:24:05.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.54,0:24:08.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}There’s something even stranger about this room!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.92,0:24:10.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Look at the shelves!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.63,0:24:13.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}The dolls{action figures?}, the miniature cars and the books…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.18,0:24:15.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}They’re all upside-down!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.18,0:24:16.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.76,0:24:19.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.14,0:24:24.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Haramoto-san{\i0} didn’t turn\N them upside down, the killer did!
